data.title: GRO MARRIAGE INDEX 1950 - 1999
data.text:
GRO MARRIAGE INDEX 1950 - 1999

This index includes all ENEVER marriages indexed by the General Register Office (GRO) for the period 1950 through 1999.

For each entry is given the Year and Quarter the marriage was registered the surname and forenames the spouse's name if known plus the registration district volume and page number of the entry. Quarters are 1 = Jan - Mar; 2 = Apr - June; 3 = July - Sept; 4 = Oct - Dec.

The information was transcribed from the LDS microfilms and fiche. Some of these were difficult to read. One should check references if possible before ordering certficates.

See also 1837 - 1899 and 1900 - 1949

Return to Home.
